fields.title: About
fields.content:
The Industry Network Village. The meaning of Village is a self-contained district; Community within a town or city, regarded as having features characteristic of village life. TINVILLE is a virtual hub to network your product and to shop within your network. TINVILLE is where up and coming designers as well as established designers can build up their own network of buyers and people who enjoy their work and also keep them updated on any new designs they want to introduce to their network of followers. Also, share their updates with all and any social networking sites that they use to market themselves. TINVILLE is also for shoppers who want to build a network of the designer they enjoy most while having the ability to share what they like about the designers in other social networking sites.

Mission: Our mission at TINVILLE is to connect designers and sellers and have them become an inhabitant of our village. While so many people get lost when going to a mall or store trying to find what they really want. In our village you can find the best styles from untouched talent in the industry.

fields.title: Policies
fields.content:
1. Tinville Venue

Tinville stages a venue which allow users to exhibit their merchandise while complying with Tinville policies. Tinville policies offer, sell and buy certain goods within a fixed-price format. Tinville intention is not directly involved in the transaction between buyers and sellers. As a result, Tinville has no marginal control over the quality, safety, morality or legal cause of any aspect of the items listed; the truth or accuracy of the listings. The ability of sellers to sell items or the ability of buyers to pay for items. Tinville does not pre-screen users or the content or information provided by users. Tinville cannot ensure that a buyer/client or seller/trader will actually complete a transaction.
